+# Trace Reference Correctness Standards
+
+This table compares the correctness criteria used by three sources:
+
+- Unit-test source: the closest existing FlashInfer API unit test under `tests/`.
+- Old trace: the monolithic `tests/trace/test_reference_correctness.py` standard before the per-API split.
+- New trace: the current per-API `tests/trace/test_*_reference_correctness.py` standard.
+
+Every current reference test file collects at least two shape cases.
